ivestream-cancelled-3474046">由于制作问题而被取消</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kanye-west-reportedly-preparing-to-drop-new-music-imminently-3490252">据报道，韦斯特还准备“立即”放弃新音乐</a>。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/nicki-minaj-on-not-letting-kanye-west-feature-on-right-thru-me-dumbest-decision-i-ever-made-pink-friday-3483304">尼基·米娜 (Nicki Minaj) 表示坎耶·维斯特 (Kanye West) 不出演《Right Thru Me》是“我做过的最愚蠢的决定”，该帖子</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
